{"tid":1363770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"家陣應該出通碟比班狗叫佢地確保遊行人士安全","createTime":"2019-07-25T08:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T08:46:52.000Z","uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0bb39689f1db2bfbc9f092f28533d8b55673b299","tid":1363770,"uid":36775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:41:35.000Z","msg":"狗擺明唔想得失兩邊先遲半粒鐘出反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n1. 暗示示威者去遊行實際上無違法（48小時內出反對書先有效）<br />\n2. 同鄉黑交代有做野<br />\n<br />\n狗隻唔想上身，就梗加要綁死佢地<br />\n開宗明義唔會入圍村範圍同燒村，就好似劉二世條底線咁<br />\n唔會主動攻擊，只係比人打先會反擊，以直報怨<br />\n到時班狗一定上曬失職責任，保護市民不力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14497db705348c59405d55c8fcf8cec5cd4c2d01","tid":1363770,"uid":100775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:44:49.000Z","msg":"但點先證明到佢係遲半粒鐘"},{"pid":"7317848a64c689927adb1f48eeb6c5731dd14b1f","tid":1363770,"uid":23468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:45:00.000Z","msg":"講咗7日內提出嘅遊行申請，可以24小時內反對囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed6f0c089f3d6c9839613f1a51845a4ef08fa4ce","tid":1363770,"uid":279085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:46:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzfNKZRPQHZk&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUZB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=6ca07e5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk</a>"},{"pid":"5bce4057b30a7eaada59f2e53cab318bdac31982","tid":1363770,"uid":23919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:46:52.000Z","msg":"元朗呢個CASE 係24小時前就可以反對啊"}]}